WEBVTT

00:06.571 --> 00:10.575
[ HORNS HONKING,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

00:10.575 --> 00:12.055
MRS. HARBACH.

00:12.055 --> 00:14.840
HI. I'M JACQUI.
I'M MR. HERTZBERG'S ASSISTANT.

00:14.840 --> 00:16.320
OH, THANK YOU
FOR MEETING ME.

00:16.320 --> 00:18.453
OF COURSE. IF YOU'LL
JUST FOLLOW ME THIS WAY.

00:27.244 --> 00:32.032
I-I WAS SO SORRY TO HEAR
ABOUT GRANDPA'S DEATH.

00:32.032 --> 00:33.946
I-I'M STILL IN SHOCK.

00:33.946 --> 00:38.081
JAMES HAD CANCER, ERICH.
HE WAS DYING.

00:38.081 --> 00:41.911
I'M SURE HE WAS
JUST SICK AND TIRED

00:41.911 --> 00:43.913
OF BEING SICK AND TIRED.

00:43.913 --> 00:45.349
YEAH.

00:45.349 --> 00:48.048
STILL, IT MUST HAVE BEEN
QUITE THE ORDEAL.

00:48.048 --> 00:49.745
MY GOODNESS, IT WAS NOTHING

00:49.745 --> 00:52.139
COMPARED TO WHAT
YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH.

00:53.879 --> 00:58.101
AFTER WE FIRST MET,
GRANDPA REACHED OUT TO ME.

00:58.101 --> 00:59.363
WERE YOU AWARE?

00:59.363 --> 01:00.669
NO.

01:00.669 --> 01:02.279
I THINK HE WANTED IT
TO BE A SURPRISE.

01:02.279 --> 01:05.369
HE WAS WAITING
FOR YOUR BIRTHDAY.

01:09.156 --> 01:10.766
W-WHAT IS THIS?

01:10.766 --> 01:13.334
IT'S A BANK ACCOUNT
MADE IN YOUR NAME,

01:13.334 --> 01:15.379
ESTABLISHED
BY YOUR HUSBAND.

01:15.379 --> 01:17.425
DAVID HELPED GRANDPA
SET IT UP.

01:17.425 --> 01:19.557
HE WANTED TO MAKE SURE
THAT YOU

01:19.557 --> 01:22.212
WERE PROPERLY TAKEN CARE OF
AFTER HIS DEATH.

01:22.212 --> 01:24.301
BUT WE DON'T HAVE
ANY MONEY.

01:24.301 --> 01:27.391
YOU DO NOW.
TAKE A LOOK.

01:29.785 --> 01:33.049
HALF A MILLION DOLLARS?

01:53.069 --> 01:55.071
THANK YOU.

01:55.071 --> 01:57.769
[ GUNSHOT ]

01:57.769 --> 02:00.903
SAMMY'S USING
THE WATER TUB.

02:00.903 --> 02:02.731
[ GUNSHOT ]

02:02.731 --> 02:05.299
SO, THIS IS OUR TEST BULLET

02:05.299 --> 02:08.040
FROM THE GUN YOU FOUND
ON JAMES HARBACH.

02:08.040 --> 02:10.521
THIS IS THE BULLET
THAT WAS EMBEDDED

02:10.521 --> 02:13.133
IN KEVIN NEYERS'
PARIETAL BONE.

02:13.133 --> 02:16.397
SAME CALIBER, SAME LANDS,
SAME GROOVES, SAME GUN.

02:16.397 --> 02:17.963
SO YOU RAN IT
THROUGH CLETS?

02:17.963 --> 02:19.791
TWICE.
THE GUN IS CLEAN.

02:19.791 --> 02:21.532
THERE'S NO RECORD OF ITS SALE,
NO LISTING IN THE DATABASE.

02:21.532 --> 02:23.491
IT'S ICE-COLD.

02:23.491 --> 02:26.102
AS FAR AS THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT
IS CONCERNED, IT DOESN'T EXIST.

02:26.102 --> 02:28.060
HMM.

02:32.804 --> 02:35.329
IT'S THE GRIPS
THAT CAUGHT MY EYE.

02:35.329 --> 02:38.506
SEE THAT NUMBER IN THE CORNER
THERE? 1970?

02:41.465 --> 02:43.206
LET ME SEE.
YEAH.

02:43.206 --> 02:47.645
1970. FOUR-INCH .357.

02:47.645 --> 02:49.908
NOW, IS THIS THE YEAR
IT WAS MANUFACTURED?

02:49.908 --> 02:51.649
THAT WAS MY FIRST INSTINCT,
AS WELL,

02:51.649 --> 02:54.870
BUT I RAN THE GUN AND THE GRIPS
AGAINST FACTORY LOGS.

02:54.870 --> 02:57.002
THEY WEREN'T MANUFACTURED
TILL '75.

02:57.002 --> 02:58.830
YEAH, MY DAD
HAD ONE OF THESE.

02:58.830 --> 03:01.006
HE USED TO SCRATCH
HIS STAR NUMBER

03:01.006 --> 03:02.965
INTO THE GRIP
JUST LIKE THAT.

03:02.965 --> 03:04.967
OH, SO THAT'S NOT A YEAR.
THAT'S -- THAT'S A STAR NUMBER?

03:04.967 --> 03:07.665
YEAH. BUT YOU SAID
THIS GUN'S COLD, RIGHT?

03:07.665 --> 03:10.668
SO, HOW WOULD YOU GET
AN S.F.P.D. WEAPON OUT
OF THE FEDERAL DATABASE?

03:10.668 --> 03:13.018
YOU WOULDN'T HAVE TO
IF IT WAS NEVER IN THERE.

03:13.018 --> 03:15.543
YOU SEE, WHEN THIS GUN
WAS ISSUED,

03:15.543 --> 03:18.850
THE S.F.P.D. ONLY REGISTERED
WEAPONS INTERNALLY.

03:18.850 --> 03:20.939
WE DIDN'T REGISTER WITH THE FEDS
UNTIL THE EARLY '80s.

03:20.939 --> 03:23.072
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]EXCUSE ME.

03:23.072 --> 03:25.727
YEAH.

03:25.727 --> 03:29.252
SO IT'S GOT TO BE SALTER,
RIGHT?

03:29.252 --> 03:31.559
NO, 1970 --
THAT'S NOT SALTER.

03:31.559 --> 03:32.995
HIS NUMBER IS 1900.

03:32.995 --> 03:34.692
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

03:34.692 --> 03:36.694
HE WAS MY FIRST SERGEANT
COMING OUT OF THE ACADEMY.

03:36.694 --> 03:38.566
I HAD TO WRITE
HIS DAMN NUMBER DOWN

03:38.566 --> 03:41.133
EVERY TIME I FILLED OUT A REPORT
FOR LIKE THREE YEARS,

03:41.133 --> 03:42.613
SO, UNH-UNH, I WOULD KNOW.

03:42.613 --> 03:47.052
1900 -- SALTER.
1970 -- THAT'S NAVARRO.

03:47.052 --> 03:49.054
Navarro: I GOT A BERETTA
AS A ROOKIE IN '95,

03:49.054 --> 03:51.535
BUT AFTER THE RECALL WAS ISSUED
A SIG, JUST LIKE YOU.

03:51.535 --> 03:53.668
TWO GUNS. BOTH AUTOMATICS.
THAT'S IT.

03:53.668 --> 03:55.452
DO YOU REMEMBER THE LAST GUY
WHO HAD YOUR STAR?

03:55.452 --> 03:57.976
HOWARD...SOMETHING.

03:57.976 --> 04:01.241
UH...I THINK HE GOT FIRED.

04:04.418 --> 04:07.159
HOWARD TOOMEY.

04:07.159 --> 04:10.554
OKAY, YEAH, HE HAD IT
FROM '76 TO '96.

04:10.554 --> 04:11.990
LOOKS LIKE HE GOT IT
FROM HIS DAD.

04:11.990 --> 04:15.994
STEVEN TOOMEY HAD STAR 1970
DATING BACK TO 1942.

04:15.994 --> 04:19.607
HE MADE IT TO DEPUTY
CHIEF, RAN THE METRO
DIVISION. DECEASED.

04:19.607 --> 04:22.914
HIS SON HOWARD RAN
THE ALCOHOL LICENSING UNIT,

04:22.914 --> 04:24.525
AND YOU'RE RIGHT --

04:24.525 --> 04:27.832
HOWARD TOOMEY WAS FIRED
IN 1996 AT AGE 49.

04:27.832 --> 04:32.184
OKAY, SO IF HE WAS 49
IN '96, THEN...

04:32.184 --> 04:34.056
THAT MEANS HE'S 67 NOW.67.

04:34.056 --> 04:37.277
DIDN'T D-HOP SAY THAT THE GUY
THAT KILLED KEVIN NEYERS

04:37.277 --> 04:39.279
WAS KIND OF OLD?YEAH, BUT, LOOK,

04:39.279 --> 04:41.542
H-HERE'S THE PROBLEM --
ACCORDING TO THE LAB,

04:41.542 --> 04:43.239
HARBACH DEFINITELY WROTE
THE NOTE.

04:43.239 --> 04:45.241
I MEAN, IT'S HIS HANDWRITING,
IT'S HIS PEN,

04:45.241 --> 04:47.025
AND JAMES HARBACH'S
SUICIDE NOTE SAYS

04:47.025 --> 04:48.418
THAT HE KILLED
KEVIN NEYERS.

04:48.418 --> 04:50.420
DID THE LAB FIND
ANY INDENTS?

04:50.420 --> 04:52.509
MM. NOT THAT I'M AWARE OF.

04:52.509 --> 04:54.772
ALL RIGHT,
MAYBE THE NOTE

04:54.772 --> 04:58.080
WASN'T THE LAST THING
THAT HARBACH WROTE.

04:58.080 --> 04:59.821
Hildy: WELL, ISN'T ANALYZING
FOR INDENTS

04:59.821 --> 05:01.997
KIND OF
STANDARD PROCEDURE?

05:01.997 --> 05:03.520
[ LAUGHTER ]

05:03.520 --> 05:06.697
THERE'S NOTHING
REALLY, UH, STANDARD PROCEDURE

05:06.697 --> 05:08.264
ABOUT OUR
HANDWRITING EXPERT.

05:08.264 --> 05:11.354
HERE WE GO.Navarro:
LITTLE MISS MOLLY.

05:11.354 --> 05:14.879
[ SIREN WAILS ]

05:14.879 --> 05:16.620
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

05:16.620 --> 05:19.754
WELL, THIS IS THE ADDRESS.
LOOKS LIKE A HALFWAY HOUSE.

05:19.754 --> 05:22.713
SOBER LIVING.

05:22.713 --> 05:24.759
NOT EVERY COP
LIVES HAPPILY EVER AFTER.

05:24.759 --> 05:26.804
LET'S JUST HOPE
THE GUY'S NOT DRUNK.

05:29.285 --> 05:31.113
HOWARD TOOMEY?

05:31.113 --> 05:32.854
DEPENDS.

05:34.812 --> 05:37.206
MAY I HELP YOU?YEAH, UH,

05:37.206 --> 05:39.164
WE JUST NEED TO
SPEAK WITH MR. TOOMEY
FOR A COUPLE MINUTES.

05:39.164 --> 05:40.165
ABSOLUTELY.

05:40.165 --> 05:41.515
GOPHER, WHY DON'T YOU

05:41.515 --> 05:44.082
GO HELP MARCIE
IN THE KITCHEN?

05:44.082 --> 05:47.172
YEAH, I DRANK LIKE A FISH
WHEN I WAS A COP.

05:47.172 --> 05:48.913
MY ASSIGNMENT DIDN'T HELP.

05:48.913 --> 05:51.655
I ENDED UP DRINKING MYSELF
OFF THE FORCE.

05:51.655 --> 05:53.657
BACK THEN,
THAT WAS NO SMALL FEAT.

05:53.657 --> 05:55.442
EVERYONE DRANK
ALL THE TIME.

05:55.442 --> 05:57.269
AND HOW LONG HAVE YOU,
UH, WORKED HERE?

05:57.269 --> 05:58.923
AS A COUNSELOR?YEAH.

05:58.923 --> 06:00.403
EIGHT YEARS.

06:00.403 --> 06:02.797
AND YOU LIVE HERE?FIVE NIGHTS A WEEK.

06:02.797 --> 06:04.364
I DON'T MIND IT, THOUGH.

06:04.364 --> 06:05.669
IT'S NICE SEEING GUYS
TURN THEIR LIFE AROUND.

06:05.669 --> 06:08.759
SO, SHOW ME THIS GUN.

06:08.759 --> 06:11.022
OKAY,
AS YOU CAN SEE THERE,

06:11.022 --> 06:14.591
THE NUMBER'S BEEN SCRATCHED
ON THE INSIDE HANDLE.

06:17.551 --> 06:19.988
THAT'S MY NUMBER,
BUT THAT'S NOT MY GUN.

06:19.988 --> 06:23.034
I WAS ISSUED A SIX-INCH
AS A ROOKIE, NOT A FOUR-INCH.

06:23.034 --> 06:24.906
DON'T ALL ROOKIES
GET A FOUR-INCH?

06:24.906 --> 06:26.516
MY DAD WAS DEPUTY CHIEF.

06:26.516 --> 06:28.692
HE PULLED STRINGS TO MAKE SURE
I GOT THE BIG GUN.

06:28.692 --> 06:30.999
THAT SIX-INCH .357 WAS
THE ONLY FIREARM I CARRIED

06:30.999 --> 06:32.914
UNTIL WE SWITCHED
TO AUTOMATICS.

06:32.914 --> 06:34.219
SO YOU DON'T THINK
THERE'S ANY WAY

06:34.219 --> 06:35.525
THAT THAT COULD BE
YOUR DAD'S GUN?

06:35.525 --> 06:37.048
OH, NO WAY.
HE CARRIED A COLT .45.

06:37.048 --> 06:39.224
ANY CHANCE SOMEONE ELSE
COULD HAVE HAD THE STAR NUMBER

06:39.224 --> 06:40.443
IN BETWEEN YOU
AND YOUR FATHER?

06:41.792 --> 06:44.752
COME TO THINK OF IT,
THERE WAS ANOTHER GUY.

06:44.752 --> 06:47.798
WHEN DAD RETIRED, I HAD TO
HORSE-TRADE HIM FOR THE NUMBER,

06:47.798 --> 06:49.931
AND HE ONLY HAD IT
A COUPLE OF WEEKS.

06:49.931 --> 06:51.802
PLEASE TELL ME
YOU REMEMBER HIS NAME.

06:51.802 --> 06:53.804
NO.

06:53.804 --> 06:56.720
BUT I REMEMBER THAT HE WAS
A REAL HOTSHOT,

06:56.720 --> 06:58.505
AND I REMEMBER THAT I HAD

06:58.505 --> 07:01.246
TO GIVE UP THIS GREAT NUMBER
FOR IT.

07:01.246 --> 07:02.596
WHAT WAS IT?

07:02.596 --> 07:05.381
UH...OH! TURN OF THE CENTURY --
1900.

07:05.381 --> 07:07.514
THAT'S SALTER.

07:07.514 --> 07:10.473
JIMMY SALTER.
THAT'S THE GUY.

07:12.519 --> 07:15.826
SO YOU STOLE THE GUN
FROM THE DEPARTMENT?

07:15.826 --> 07:18.916
HOW MANY GUNS DO YOU HAVE,
TERRY? GIVE ME A BREAK.

07:18.916 --> 07:21.092
THINGS WERE DIFFERENT
BACK THEN.

07:21.092 --> 07:23.530
THE RANGEMASTER WAS
A FRIEND OF MINE.

07:23.530 --> 07:25.140
EVERYBODY TRIED TO KEEP
THEIR GUNS.

07:25.140 --> 07:26.620
AND YOU WERE
SUCCESSFUL, RIGHT?

07:26.620 --> 07:29.013
SO THIS IS YOUR .357? YES?

07:31.189 --> 07:36.717
IT USED TO BE.
IT'S MY ROOKIE PISTOL.

07:36.717 --> 07:38.893
AND NOW IT TURNS UP
AS A MURDER WEAPON

07:38.893 --> 07:40.764
USED TO KILL
YOUR BOSS' FATHER.

07:40.764 --> 07:42.766
THAT'S A HELL
OF A COINCIDENCE.

07:42.766 --> 07:45.465
I DIDN'T SAY IT WAS
A COINCIDENCE.

07:45.465 --> 07:49.556
I HAVE NO IDEA HOW IT ENDED UP
IN JAMES HARBACH'S HANDS.

07:49.556 --> 07:53.298
I HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH THAT.

07:53.298 --> 07:54.952
I GOT AN IDEA WHO DID.

07:59.740 --> 08:02.699
YOU'RE QUITTING?
WHAT THE HELL? WHY?

08:05.049 --> 08:07.965
WHATEVER HAPPENED TO THAT GUN
I GAVE YOU, ERICH?

08:07.965 --> 08:10.315
WHAT GUN?

08:10.315 --> 08:14.842
COME ON.
THAT LITTLE FOUR-INCH .357.

08:14.842 --> 08:18.323
THE GUN THAT WAS USED
TO KILL KEVIN NEYERS.

08:18.323 --> 08:21.501
YOU NEVER GAVE ME ANY GUN.

08:21.501 --> 08:24.808
YOU'RE KIDDING, RIGHT?

08:30.379 --> 08:33.991
JIMMY,
ARE YOU WEARING A WIRE?

08:33.991 --> 08:38.648
WOULD YOU DO THAT TO ME?
TURN ON ME LIKE THAT?

08:38.648 --> 08:42.304
I'VE BEEN NOTHING
BUT GOOD TO YOU.

08:47.048 --> 08:51.531
IT'S BEEN AN ADVENTURE, ERICH.
THAT'S FOR SURE.

08:53.054 --> 08:56.405
GOOD LUCK, KID.
YOU'RE GONNA NEED IT.

09:03.847 --> 09:05.980
[ SIGHS ]

09:14.336 --> 09:16.164
[ HORNS HONKING ]

09:16.164 --> 09:18.906
[ BELL DINGS ]

09:18.906 --> 09:20.951
ALL RIGHT,
SO SALTER GOT THE GUN TO BLUNT.

09:20.951 --> 09:24.128
HARBACH USED THE GUN
TO KILL NEYERS.

09:24.128 --> 09:26.261
SO, AT A MINIMUM,
BLUNT IS AN ACCESSORY.

09:26.261 --> 09:27.828
WELL, NOW WHEN YOU'VE GOT
A FOUR-YEAR GAP

09:27.828 --> 09:29.264
BETWEEN WHEN SALTER GAVE HIM
THE GUN

09:29.264 --> 09:31.048
AND WHEN WE FOUND IT
ON HARBACH --

09:31.048 --> 09:33.616
I MEAN, EVEN IF BLUNT ADMITS
HE GAVE THE GUN TO HARBACH,

09:33.616 --> 09:36.140
HE COULD STILL CLAIM IT WAS
FOR HOME PROTECTION

09:36.140 --> 09:39.317
AND THAT HE KNEW NOTHING OF THE
OLD MAN'S PLANS TO KILL NEYERS.

09:39.317 --> 09:41.363
I MEAN, INDIVIDUALLY,
EVERY PIECE OF EVIDENCE

09:41.363 --> 09:42.930
COULD BE EXPLAINED AWAY
BY BLUNT.

09:42.930 --> 09:44.627
WELL, EVERYTHING
EXCEPT THE TIMING.

09:44.627 --> 09:46.281
I MEAN,
LET'S THINK ABOUT THIS.

09:46.281 --> 09:48.022
SO, WITHIN A TWO-MONTH SPAN,

09:48.022 --> 09:50.546
HARBACH MEETS BLUNT
FOR THE FIRST TIME,

09:50.546 --> 09:52.113
ENDS UP WITH BLUNT'S GUN,

09:52.113 --> 09:54.245
KILLS BLUNT'S
BIOLOGICAL FATHER

09:54.245 --> 09:56.421
WITHIN A WEEK
OF APPLSN's I.P.O.

09:56.421 --> 09:59.120
YEAH, WE JUST NEED MORE EVIDENCE
CONNECTING THOSE DOTS.

09:59.120 --> 10:01.688
WELL, SPEAK OF THE DEVIL.
HERE IT COMES.

10:01.688 --> 10:04.778
HEY, MOLLY.
HUH. WHAT DO YOU GOT FOR US?

10:04.778 --> 10:07.824
HE USED A FOUNTAIN PEN,
SO THE IMPRINTS WERE SETTLED.

10:07.824 --> 10:09.260
T-T-THIS ONE WAS CLEAREST,

10:09.260 --> 10:11.262
WHICH MEANS IT
WAS PROBABLY WRITTEN

10:11.262 --> 10:13.090
ON THE PREVIOUS SHEET
OF PAPER.

10:15.963 --> 10:17.007
SEÑOR.

10:17.007 --> 10:20.402
EXCUSE ME.
THANKS, MOL.

10:20.402 --> 10:21.969
AH, "DEAR BETTY,

10:21.969 --> 10:24.319
"WHEN YOU FIND THIS NOTE,
CALL DAVID HERTZBERG.

10:24.319 --> 10:27.801
"YOU CAN TRUST HIM.
HE'LL TAKE CARE OF YOU.

10:27.801 --> 10:30.499
I LOVE YOU. JAMES."

10:30.499 --> 10:32.762
THE SAGA CONTINUES.
RIGHT?

10:32.762 --> 10:36.070
OKAY. LET'S START
WITH MRS. HARBACH.

10:36.070 --> 10:38.899
THE MOMENT WE GO TO HERTZBERG,
WE'RE GOING TO BLUNT.

10:38.899 --> 10:41.466
ALL RIGHT, WELL, IF BETTY
HARBACH'S SPEAKING TO HERTZBERG,

10:41.466 --> 10:43.555
ANYTHING WE TELL HER
IS GONNA GET BACK TO HIM.

10:43.555 --> 10:44.992
ARE WE RUNNING THIS
BY PEREZ?

10:44.992 --> 10:48.212
WE DON'T WORK FOR PEREZ.
THIS IS MY CALL.

10:50.650 --> 10:53.435
HEY, MOL. AH.

10:54.697 --> 10:56.830
UH, THANK YOU,
MISS MOLLY.

11:05.708 --> 11:08.929
Betty: OH, IT'S
JUST A SECURITY SYSTEM.

11:08.929 --> 11:11.714
Terry: WELL, I MEAN, YOU GOT
CAMERAS, SENSORS, INFRARED.

11:11.714 --> 11:14.369
THAT'S A PRETTY SOPHISTICATED
SECURITY SYSTEM.

11:14.369 --> 11:17.851
I-I GOT THE FIVE-STAR ELECTRONIC
HOME-BUNKER SYSTEM.

11:17.851 --> 11:19.069
TOP OF THE LINE.

11:19.069 --> 11:20.157
LOOKS EXPENSIVE.

11:20.157 --> 11:21.724
OH, THEY GAVE ME
A GOOD DEAL.

11:21.724 --> 11:24.161
I THINK
THEY FELT SORRY FOR ME.

11:24.161 --> 11:26.816
I HAVEN'T LIVED ALONE
IN 50 YEARS.

11:26.816 --> 11:29.471
CAN WE COME IN? WE JUST HAVE
A COUPLE QUESTIONS FOR YOU.

11:29.471 --> 11:31.255
I-I-I-I'M SORRY.

11:31.255 --> 11:33.736
I WISH I COULD HELP YOU,

11:33.736 --> 11:37.566
BUT...MY LAWYER ADVISED ME
NOT TO SPEAK TO THE POLICE.

11:37.566 --> 11:40.177
WE KNOW ABOUT THE NOTE,
MRS. HARBACH --

11:40.177 --> 11:43.050
THE ONE YOUR HUSBAND LEFT
INSTRUCTING YOU TO SPEAK
WITH DAVID HERTZBERG.

11:43.050 --> 11:44.747
IS HE YOUR LAWYER?

11:44.747 --> 11:48.272
I-I-I'M SORRY. I-I HAVE
TO CLOSE THE DOOR NOW.

11:48.272 --> 11:51.362
OKAY. IF YOU CLOSE
THE DOOR, WE'LL RETURN
WITH A SEARCH WARRANT.

11:52.363 --> 11:54.757
[ SIGHS ]

11:54.757 --> 11:56.498
YOU CAN SEARCH
HIGH AND LOW.

11:56.498 --> 11:58.413
YOU WON'T FIND
ANYTHING IN HERE

11:58.413 --> 12:00.807
CONCERNING ANY KIND
OF CRIMINAL ACTIVITY.

12:00.807 --> 12:03.244
MY HUSBAND WOULD NEVER PUT ME
THROUGH THAT.

12:03.244 --> 12:05.986
DID YOU FIGURE OUT
WHERE HE KEPT HIS REVOLVER?

12:05.986 --> 12:07.552
NO, I HAVEN'T.

12:07.552 --> 12:10.338
LIKE I SAID BEFORE,
I DON'T KNOW WHERE HE GOT IT,

12:10.338 --> 12:12.775
AND I DON'T KNOW
WHERE HE KEPT IT.

12:12.775 --> 12:14.516
WELL, HE GOT IT
FROM ERICH BLUNT.

12:14.516 --> 12:18.999
THEY WARNED ME YOU MIGHT TRY
TO DO SOMETHING LIKE THIS,

12:18.999 --> 12:21.784
GET ME TO TURN
ON MY GRANDSON.

12:21.784 --> 12:23.830
WELL, WE'RE NOT TRYING
TO DO ANYTHING.

12:23.830 --> 12:25.396
WE'RE JUST TELLING YOU
THE FACTS.

12:25.396 --> 12:27.050
THE GUN THEY FOUND
ON YOUR HUSBAND --

12:27.050 --> 12:28.748
THE GUN THAT KILLED
KEVIN NEYERS --

12:28.748 --> 12:30.097
BELONGED TO ERICH BLUNT.

12:30.097 --> 12:32.229
M-MR. HERTZBERG TOLD ME
TO CALL HIM

12:32.229 --> 12:34.014
IN A SITUATION
LIKE THIS.

12:34.014 --> 12:35.450
OF COURSE HE DID.

12:35.450 --> 12:38.018
HIS CLIENT GAVE YOUR HUSBAND
A MURDER WEAPON.

12:38.018 --> 12:39.323
WHY DID YOUR HUSBAND
WANT YOU

12:39.323 --> 12:40.934
TO SEE MR. HERTZBERG
AFTER HE DIED?

12:42.805 --> 12:44.807
[ SIGHS ]

12:44.807 --> 12:47.723
BECAUSE JAMES LEFT ME
SOME MONEY.

12:47.723 --> 12:51.205
ERICH GAVE IT TO HIM TO TAKE
CARE OF ME AFTER HIS DEATH.

12:51.205 --> 12:53.294
MR. HERTZBERG SET IT UP.

12:53.294 --> 12:54.599
WHEN DID THEY TELL YOU?

12:54.599 --> 12:56.645
DAY BEFORE YESTERDAY.

12:56.645 --> 12:58.212
DID THEY TELL YOU
HOW MUCH MONEY?

13:00.649 --> 13:02.607
HALF A MILLION DOLLARS.

13:05.915 --> 13:10.964
THEY GAVE ME THIS PORTFOLIO
WITH ALL THE INFORMATION.

13:13.967 --> 13:16.447
THANK YOU.

13:16.447 --> 13:17.797
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

13:21.191 --> 13:24.368
LOOKS LIKE THIS ACCOUNT
WAS SET UP BACK IN MAY.

13:24.368 --> 13:28.068
WHY WOULD THEY HAVE WAITED
SO LONG TO TELL YOU ABOUT IT?

13:28.068 --> 13:31.332
JAMES WANTED TO SURPRISE ME.
THAT'S WHAT ERICH SAID.

13:31.332 --> 13:32.899
DID YOU SPEND ANY OF IT?

13:32.899 --> 13:35.989
UH, $10,000
FOR THE SECURITY SYSTEM.

13:35.989 --> 13:38.208
I PUT IT ON THE DEBIT CARD.

13:38.208 --> 13:41.385
WELL, THERE'S ANOTHER WITHDRAWAL
LISTED RIGHT HERE.

13:41.385 --> 13:42.996
OH, THE $1,300?

13:42.996 --> 13:45.172
I NOTICED THAT.
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THAT WAS FOR.

13:45.172 --> 13:46.608
THE WITHDRAWAL WAS MADE

13:46.608 --> 13:48.740
TWO DAYS AFTER THE ACCOUNT
WAS FIRST OPENED.

13:48.740 --> 13:51.091
THAT'S A WEEK BEFORE NEYERS
WAS KILLED.

13:51.091 --> 13:53.528
I'M NOT FOLLOWING.

13:55.965 --> 13:58.359
DO YOU KNOW WHAT,
UM, FENTANYL IS?

13:59.926 --> 14:01.884
THE PAIN MEDICATION?
SURE.

14:01.884 --> 14:05.670
IT'S THE ONLY THING THAT GAVE
JAMES ANY RELIEF TOWARD THE END.

14:24.689 --> 14:25.865
TERRY!

14:25.865 --> 14:28.476
HEY, MAN.

14:28.476 --> 14:32.697
THOUGHT YOU WERE TRYING TO BREAK
IN TO MY PAD FOR A SECOND.

14:32.697 --> 14:36.092
WHY? 'CAUSE, UH --
'CAUSE I'M BLACK?

14:36.092 --> 14:38.051
NO, 'CAUSE YOU WERE RATTLING
ON MY WINDOW.

14:38.051 --> 14:39.530
[ Chuckling ]
JUST PLAYING WITH YOU, MAN.

14:39.530 --> 14:41.532
I'M JUST PLAYING.

14:41.532 --> 14:43.012
THAT'S A NICE BIKE.

14:43.012 --> 14:46.537
WAIT UNTIL I GET
THE ENGINE FIXED.

14:46.537 --> 14:48.104
IT'S A BEAST.

14:48.104 --> 14:50.324
JUST HOPE IT DOESN'T FALL APART
ON THE HIGHWAY.

14:50.324 --> 14:53.109
WHERE YOU OFF TO?
SACRAMENTO.

14:53.109 --> 14:54.676
COOL, COOL.

14:54.676 --> 14:56.547
GONNA GO VISIT YOUR GIRL
OR SOMETHING?

14:56.547 --> 14:58.158
NO, NO, JUST FAMILY.

14:58.158 --> 15:01.683
I'M THINKING OF MOVING UP THERE,
YOU KNOW, STARTING OVER.

15:01.683 --> 15:04.294
MY UNCLE'S A FOREMAN
AT A BATTERY FACTORY.

15:04.294 --> 15:06.296
HE GOT ME A JOB INTERVIEW.

15:06.296 --> 15:09.212
LOOK AT YOU. CITIZEN WALTON.
ALL RIGHT.

15:09.212 --> 15:12.172
YEAH, THANKS TO YOU, I GOT
A SECOND CHANCE, YOU KNOW.

15:12.172 --> 15:13.651
DOESN'T HAPPEN EVERY DAY.

15:13.651 --> 15:16.089
I AIN'T PLANNING ON WASTING IT,
YOU KNOW?

15:16.089 --> 15:18.265
THAT'S GOOD.

15:18.265 --> 15:20.049
I GOT A FAVOR
TO ASK OF YOU.

15:20.049 --> 15:22.617
WE'RE GETTING PRETTY CLOSE
ON THIS NEYERS CASE.

15:22.617 --> 15:25.098
WANTED TO ASK YOU -- HOW MUCH
DID NEYERS GIVE YOU

15:25.098 --> 15:27.230
FOR THAT BAG OF FENTANYL
THAT YOU DELIVERED

15:27.230 --> 15:28.579
THE DAY HE WAS KILLED?

15:28.579 --> 15:31.104
20 POPS AT 50,

15:31.104 --> 15:33.715
PLUS A COUPLE
OF TRANSDERMAL PATCHES...

15:33.715 --> 15:35.151
$1,300.

15:35.151 --> 15:36.936
NO SHIT.

15:36.936 --> 15:38.807
CASH UP FRONT.

15:38.807 --> 15:40.417
ALL RIGHT.

15:40.417 --> 15:43.725
MY MAN.
ANYTIME.

15:46.075 --> 15:47.511
CHRIS.

15:49.383 --> 15:51.211
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF.

15:51.211 --> 15:53.822
YOU, TOO, INSPECTOR.

16:01.699 --> 16:03.397
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

16:09.620 --> 16:11.883
[ BELL DINGING ]

16:11.883 --> 16:14.582
Koto: WE NEED TO UPDATE YOU ON
THE KEVIN NEYERS INVESTIGATION.

16:14.582 --> 16:16.671
WE'RE CLOSING IN
ON AN ARREST.

16:16.671 --> 16:19.021
WELL, UNLESS YOU HAVE PROOF,
YOU'RE WASTING MY TIME.

16:19.021 --> 16:21.502
WE HAVE BLUNT PAYING OFF HARBACH
AND PROVIDING THE GUN.

16:21.502 --> 16:23.286
FOR WHAT?FOR KILLING NEYERS.

16:23.286 --> 16:25.158
CAN BLUNT EXPLAIN IT
DIFFERENTLY?

16:25.158 --> 16:27.595
SURE, BUT --SEE, STOP RIGHT THERE.

16:27.595 --> 16:30.685
WHEN THE ANSWER TO THAT QUESTION
IS "NO," COME BACK TO ME.

16:30.685 --> 16:33.209
NONE OF US WANTS
TO GET BURNED TWICE.

16:33.209 --> 16:35.124
BUT WE HAVE TWICE
AS MUCH ON HIM HERE

16:35.124 --> 16:37.126
THAN WE DID
IN THE CINDY STRAUSS CASE.

16:37.126 --> 16:40.216
AND NOW WE HAVE SOMETHING EVEN
MORE IMPORTANT -- A PATTERN.

16:40.216 --> 16:43.002
YES, WE HAVE -- A PATTERN
OF ARRESTING ERICH BLUNT.

16:43.002 --> 16:44.177
A PATTERN FOR MURDER.

16:44.177 --> 16:45.352
Perez: NOT IN THE EYES
OF THE COURT.

16:45.352 --> 16:48.442
WE LOST THAT CASE.
REMEMBER?

16:48.442 --> 16:50.879
LOOK, WE WERE RIGHT THEN,
AND WE'RE RIGHT NOW.

16:50.879 --> 16:53.229
ERICH BLUNT
KILLED KEVIN NEYERS.

16:53.229 --> 16:55.188
Siletti: WHY DOES HE WANT
THIS GUY DEAD ANYWAY?

16:55.188 --> 16:56.885
WHO GIVES A SHIT?HE DOES. HE HATES HIM.

16:56.885 --> 16:59.235
HE WAS BLACKMAILING HIM
DAYS BEFORE HIS I.P.O.

16:59.235 --> 17:01.237
OKAY, SO LET'S SAY
YOU'RE RIGHT, HUH?

17:01.237 --> 17:03.413
HE HAS MOTIVE,
AND THEN HE REALIZES,

17:03.413 --> 17:04.893
"WHY DO IT YOURSELF

17:04.893 --> 17:07.330
WHEN YOU CAN PAY ANOTHER GUY
TO DO IT FOR YOU?"

17:07.330 --> 17:10.290
BUT THEN YOU'RE SAYING HE OPTS
AGAINST HIRING A PROFESSIONAL,

17:10.290 --> 17:12.509
DECIDING INSTEAD
TO ROLL THE DICE

17:12.509 --> 17:15.599
WITH A 72-YEAR-OLD LUNG-CANCER
PATIENT FROM OAKLAND

17:15.599 --> 17:17.514
WHO HE JUST MET
A FEW WEEKS AGO --

17:17.514 --> 17:22.302
A GUY WITH NO CRIMINAL RECORD,
NO EXPERIENCE, NO GUN.

17:22.302 --> 17:25.435
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S ERICH BLUNT'S
FOOLPROOF MASTER PLAN?

17:25.435 --> 17:27.916
AS OPPOSED TO YOUR MASTER PLAN
OF BEING AN ASSHOLE?

17:27.916 --> 17:29.787
[ LAUGHS ]
I'M A LAWYER, SWEETHEART.

17:29.787 --> 17:31.311
I GET PAID TO BE
AN ASSHOLE.

17:31.311 --> 17:33.052
GREAT.
JACKIE, COME ON.

17:33.052 --> 17:35.837
WE'VE GOT MORE THAN ENOUGH
EVIDENCE TO ARREST THIS GUY.

17:35.837 --> 17:38.709
I'M NOT INTERESTED IN EVIDENCE.
I NEED PROOF.

17:38.709 --> 17:41.973
NO ALTERNATE THEORIES,
NO OTHER SUSPECTS,

17:41.973 --> 17:44.759
NO SLIPPERY TIMELINES,
NO ROOM FOR INTERPRETATION.

17:44.759 --> 17:47.805
I NEED 12 CAMERAS
FROM 12 DIFFERENT ANGLES --

17:47.805 --> 17:51.940
UNDENIABLE, UNASSAILABLE,
INCONTROVERTIBLE PROOF.

17:51.940 --> 17:54.595
THE ONLY WAY I AM TAKING
ERICH BLUNT TO TRIAL AGAIN

17:54.595 --> 17:57.076
IS IF WE'VE ALREADY WON.

18:00.862 --> 18:03.386
THANK YOU.

18:10.872 --> 18:14.789
Betty: HERE. MARCH 5th.
ERICH BLUNT.

18:14.789 --> 18:16.834
THAT'S THE DAY
WE FIRST MET.

18:16.834 --> 18:19.707
OKAY. AND YOU HAVEN'T SEEN HIM
SINCE THEN?

18:19.707 --> 18:22.362
NO, NOT TILL TWO DAYS AGO.

18:22.362 --> 18:25.800
RIGHT, AND YOUR HUSBAND OPENED
UP THE ACCOUNT ON MAY 23rd.

18:27.106 --> 18:29.456
OH, SEE,
THERE'S DOLLAR SIGNS.

18:29.456 --> 18:30.979
OH, LOOK AT THAT.

18:30.979 --> 18:33.460
I THOUGHT
THOSE DOLLAR SIGNS

18:33.460 --> 18:36.332
MEANT WE OWED
THE HOSPITAL MONEY.

18:36.332 --> 18:39.379
BUT I DIDN'T ASK.
JAMES KEPT OUR BOOKS.

18:39.379 --> 18:42.947
NOW, WOULD YOUR HUSBAND GO
TO CHEMO BY HIMSELF?

18:42.947 --> 18:44.384
UH, YES, SOMETIMES.

18:44.384 --> 18:47.169
I'M SURE THAT'S WHEN HE MET
WITH ERICH.

18:47.169 --> 18:49.258
OKAY, WELL, NEYERS WAS KILLED
AROUND 2:00 A.M.,

18:49.258 --> 18:50.999
SO DON'T YOU THINK
YOU WOULD HAVE HEARD

18:50.999 --> 18:53.349
YOUR HUSBAND GET UP AND GET OUT
OF BED, LEAVE THE HOUSE?

18:53.349 --> 18:55.482
I TAKE AMBIEN TO SLEEP.

18:55.482 --> 18:59.355
JAMES COULD HAVE LED A MARCHING
BAND THROUGH OUR BEDROOM.

18:59.355 --> 19:00.835
I WOULDN'T HAVE NOTICED.

19:00.835 --> 19:02.532
OKAY.

19:02.532 --> 19:05.840
UH, I WANTED TO JUST ASK YOU
ABOUT ONE OTHER THING --

19:05.840 --> 19:07.668
THIS RIGHT HERE
ON MEMORIAL DAY.

19:07.668 --> 19:09.322
WHAT IS THAT?

19:09.322 --> 19:11.672
OH.

19:11.672 --> 19:16.198
A MAN CAME TO THE DOOR
SELLING LIFE INSURANCE.

19:16.198 --> 19:21.551
UH...JAMES WAS OUT
OF THE HOUSE -- M.I.A.

19:21.551 --> 19:25.207
OKAY, THAT'S A WEEK
BEFORE NEYERS' DEATH.RIGHT.

19:25.207 --> 19:26.730
YOU KNOW WHERE YOUR HUSBAND
WENT AT THAT TIME?

19:26.730 --> 19:28.602
NO, I DON'T.
SEEMS LIKE
YOU WERE CONCERNED

19:28.602 --> 19:30.473
'CAUSE YOU UNDERLINED IT
TWICE HERE.

19:30.473 --> 19:32.040
WELL, Y-YOU'RE RIGHT,

19:32.040 --> 19:35.522
BUT I WASN'T CONCERNED
ABOUT MY HUSBAND'S WHEREABOUTS.

19:35.522 --> 19:37.611
I WAS CONCERNED
ABOUT THE MAN ON MY PORCH.

19:37.611 --> 19:41.136
WHO SELLS INSURANCE DOOR-TO-DOOR
ON MEMORIAL DAY?

19:41.136 --> 19:43.573
WELL, IT'S A GOOD DAY
TO FIND PEOPLE AT HOME.

19:43.573 --> 19:46.228
HE SAID HE'D RESEARCHED
MY HUSBAND'S RECORDS

19:46.228 --> 19:50.101
AND THAT HE QUALIFIED
FOR A NEW GOLD-PLATED POLICY.

19:50.101 --> 19:53.540
JAMES HAD ALREADY BEEN DIAGNOSED
WITH LUNG CANCER.

19:53.540 --> 19:55.019
DID THIS INSURANCE SALESMAN

19:55.019 --> 19:57.065
LEAVE A CARD OR A NUMBER
OR ANYTHING LIKE THAT?

19:57.065 --> 19:58.327
NO.

19:58.327 --> 20:00.590
SOON AS HE HEARD JAMES
WASN'T HOME,

20:00.590 --> 20:03.593
HE GOT IN HIS SHINY RED
SPORTS CAR AND SPED OFF.

20:44.373 --> 20:45.548
YES.

20:45.548 --> 20:46.636
[ BOTH PANTING ]

20:46.636 --> 20:48.638
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

20:51.511 --> 20:53.426
I'M GONNA KILL
WHOEVER THIS IS.

20:53.426 --> 20:56.255
WILKY. WHAT THE HELL?

21:01.869 --> 21:05.786
I'M NOT DONE WITH YOU.
WAIT UPSTAIRS.

21:20.017 --> 21:21.410
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

21:21.410 --> 21:23.151
WILKY, SLOW DOWN.
YOU'RE SPINNING.

21:23.151 --> 21:24.935
OH, YOU KNOW,
I'M ABOUT TO BE CHARGED

21:24.935 --> 21:26.110
AS AN ACCESSORY TO MURDER.

21:26.110 --> 21:28.765
SO I'M A LITTLE STRESSED,
YEAH.

21:28.765 --> 21:29.940
WHAT MURDER?

21:29.940 --> 21:33.161
KEVIN NEYERS.

21:33.161 --> 21:35.468
THE COPS KNOW ABOUT
THE HALF-MILLION DOLLARS

21:35.468 --> 21:38.253
YOU GAVE
TO JAMES HARBACH.

21:38.253 --> 21:39.994
SO WHAT?

21:39.994 --> 21:43.345
WELL, THEY ALSO KNOW THAT
YOU GAVE ME SALTER'S OLD GUN

21:43.345 --> 21:46.522
TO GIVE TO HARBACH TWO DAYS
BEFORE HE KILLED NEYERS.

21:47.915 --> 21:50.483
JESUS, MAN.

21:50.483 --> 21:53.224
AND THEY'RE SAYING THAT YOU PAID
YOUR GRANDFATHER TO KILL HIM,

21:53.224 --> 21:55.270
AND SO NOW BECAUSE I DELIVERED
THE GUN TO HIM,

21:55.270 --> 21:56.793
I'M AN ACCOMPLICE
IN THIS MURDER.

21:56.793 --> 21:58.882
THEY'RE -- THEY'RE --
THEY'RE COMING AFTER US!

21:58.882 --> 22:02.277
FIRST OF ALL,
THEY DON'T KNOW ANYTHING.

22:02.277 --> 22:05.019
THEY'RE JUST TRYING TO SCARE YOU
INTO IMPLICATING ME,

22:05.019 --> 22:08.065
WHICH YOU CAN'T DO BECAUSE
I NEVER GAVE YOU SALTER'S GUN.

22:08.065 --> 22:09.632
WHAT?
OF COURSE YOU DID.

22:09.632 --> 22:11.678
HOW THE HELL
WOULD I EVEN HAVE IT

22:11.678 --> 22:13.680
IF Y-YOU HADN'T
GIVEN IT TO ME?

22:13.680 --> 22:15.986
YOU GOT IT
FROM JIMMY SALTER.NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

22:15.986 --> 22:17.858
DON'T -- DON'T YOU DO THIS.

22:17.858 --> 22:20.513
YOU TOLD ME
THAT YOU WANTED THAT GUN

22:20.513 --> 22:23.385
FOR YOUR GRANDFATHER
FOR HOME PROTECTION.

22:23.385 --> 22:25.648
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME HE WAS
GONNA USE IT TO KILL A GUY.

22:30.827 --> 22:33.526
[ SIGHS ]

22:33.526 --> 22:35.876
TAKE YOUR CLOTHES OFF.

22:35.876 --> 22:38.531
W-WHAT? WHY?

22:38.531 --> 22:40.663
BECAUSE YOU'RE
WEARING A WIRE.
OH, COME ON.

22:40.663 --> 22:44.711
WILKY,
TAKE OFF YOUR CLOTHES.

22:44.711 --> 22:46.974
DO IT.

22:48.192 --> 22:49.498
[ SIGHS ]

23:08.517 --> 23:09.866
ASSHOLE.

23:18.135 --> 23:20.137
THOSE, TOO.

23:31.061 --> 23:32.889
YOU SATISFIED?

23:32.889 --> 23:34.369
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU DON'T TRUST ME

23:34.369 --> 23:36.153
AFTER EVERYTHING WE'VE BEEN
THROUGH TOGETHER.

23:36.153 --> 23:39.548
YOU FORGOT TO TAKE OFF
YOUR WATCH, WILKY.

23:41.898 --> 23:43.160
YOU GAVE ME THIS WATCH.

23:43.160 --> 23:46.250
I KNOW,
AND NOW I WANT IT BACK.

23:46.250 --> 23:50.124
[ SIGHS ]
COME ON. THIS IS NUTS.

23:50.124 --> 23:52.343
GIVE ME THE WATCH, WILKY.

24:19.414 --> 24:21.242
OH, WILKY.

24:21.242 --> 24:24.419
IT'S NOT WHAT YOU THINK.

24:24.419 --> 24:26.726
SURE, IT IS. LOOK.

24:28.423 --> 24:30.120
IT'S A BUG.

24:40.957 --> 24:42.785
[ GRUNTS ]

24:42.785 --> 24:44.308
[ SIGHS ]

24:44.308 --> 24:46.136
YOU'RE PATHETIC.

24:47.921 --> 24:49.966
[ Voice breaking ]
I HAD NO CHOICE!

24:49.966 --> 24:51.968
WRONG AGAIN, WILKY!

24:51.968 --> 24:55.145
YOU CHOSE TO STAB ME
IN THE BACK,

24:55.145 --> 24:57.974
AND AFTER ALL I'VE DONE
FOR YOU.

25:00.629 --> 25:03.806
WHAT EXACTLY HAVE YOU DONE
FOR ME, ERICH?

25:03.806 --> 25:05.678
WHAT?!

25:05.678 --> 25:09.029
LET'S SEE.
YOU STOLE CINDY FROM ME.

25:09.029 --> 25:12.989
YOU SENT MY WIFE THAT VIDEO!
YOU DESTROYED MY MARRIAGE!

25:12.989 --> 25:15.992
YOU'VE MADE ME
AN ACCOMPLICE

25:15.992 --> 25:17.951
IN A MURDER
THAT YOU BOUGHT AND PAID FOR.

25:17.951 --> 25:20.170
THAT'S WHAT YOU'VE DONE
FOR ME!

25:24.871 --> 25:28.309
[ SIGHS ]

25:28.309 --> 25:29.702
BILL.

25:29.702 --> 25:32.313
HEY, BILL.

25:34.445 --> 25:38.319
YOU'RE DELUSIONAL.
YOU ARE.

25:38.319 --> 25:40.800
NO, NO, NO, NO.
[ SNIFFLES ]

25:40.800 --> 25:43.106
WE WERE READY TO GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE.

25:43.106 --> 25:45.369
WE WERE GONNA START
A NEW LIFE TOGETHER.

25:45.369 --> 25:46.980
[ SIGHS ]
WE WERE.

25:46.980 --> 25:48.677
WELL, THEN, IT'S A GOOD THING
THAT I KILLED HER

25:48.677 --> 25:51.550
'CAUSE THAT WOULD HAVE BEEN
A HUGE MISTAKE.

25:51.550 --> 25:54.553
CINDY WAS CARRYING
YOUR CHILD.

25:54.553 --> 25:56.555
SHE WAS CARRYING
A FETUS.

25:56.555 --> 25:59.688
I TOLD HER TO GET RID OF IT,
BUT SHE REFUSED.

25:59.688 --> 26:01.168
[ SCOFFS ]

26:01.168 --> 26:03.823
COME ON, I WASN'T GONNA HAVE
A KID WITH CINDY.

26:03.823 --> 26:05.955
THAT WAS NEVER PART
OF THE PLAN.

26:05.955 --> 26:09.045
SO...

26:09.045 --> 26:11.265
I MEAN, SO, WHAT,
YOU JUST KILLED HER?

26:15.269 --> 26:17.445
LOOK AT IT LIKE THIS,
BILL --

26:17.445 --> 26:19.926
2/3 OF ALL HUMAN CONCEPTIONS

26:19.926 --> 26:23.843
ARE SPONTANEOUSLY ABORTED
BY NATURE.

26:23.843 --> 26:27.760
10 MILLION WOMEN DIE
EVERY YEAR IN CHILDBIRTH.

26:27.760 --> 26:32.068
I JUST NUDGED CINDY TOWARDS
THOSE PROBABLE OUTCOMES.

26:32.068 --> 26:35.071
RIGHT?

26:38.161 --> 26:39.902
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:39.902 --> 26:43.906
IT WAS SLOPPY,
BUT EFFECTIVE.

26:43.906 --> 26:47.606
NOW, THE WAY
THAT I KILLED MY FATHER --

26:47.606 --> 26:50.304
THAT WAS A WORK OF ART.

26:50.304 --> 26:52.698
YOU KNOW?

26:52.698 --> 26:54.308
I MADE SURE
ALL THE EVIDENCE

26:54.308 --> 26:56.136
WAS DOUBLE-SIDED,
CIRCUMSTANTIAL.

26:56.136 --> 26:59.313
SALTER GAVE ME THAT GUN
YEARS AGO FOR PROTECTION,

26:59.313 --> 27:01.924
AND I GAVE IT TO YOU
TO GIVE TO MY GRANDFATHER

27:01.924 --> 27:04.971
BECAUSE, WELL, HE LIVED

27:04.971 --> 27:07.147
IN A SHIT HOUSE
IN A SHIT NEIGHBORHOOD,

27:07.147 --> 27:10.150
AND HE -- HE COULDN'T EVEN
AFFORD A LOUSY SECURITY SYSTEM.

27:10.150 --> 27:12.065
AND AS FOR THE MONEY --

27:12.065 --> 27:15.590
HIS MEDICAL BILLS,
THEY JUST WIPED HIM OUT.

27:15.590 --> 27:16.809
HE WAS BROKE.

27:16.809 --> 27:18.724
I GAVE HIM THE MONEY

27:18.724 --> 27:23.119
SO MY GRANDMOTHER WASN'T THROWN
OUT ON THE STREETS, PENNILESS.

27:23.119 --> 27:27.123
KEVIN NEYERS WAS A WORM,
A VIRUS,

27:27.123 --> 27:30.823
A GLITCH IN THE SYSTEM.

27:30.823 --> 27:33.652
HE HAD TO BE KILLED.

27:33.652 --> 27:37.307
SO...

27:37.307 --> 27:39.396
YOU KILLED YOUR LOVER,

27:39.396 --> 27:41.834
YOU KILLED YOUR OWN CHILD,

27:41.834 --> 27:44.097
PAID YOUR GRANDFATHER
TO KILL YOUR FATHER,

27:44.097 --> 27:46.142
AND THEN HE TOOK
THE GUN YOU GAVE HIM

27:46.142 --> 27:48.797
AND TURNED IT ON HIMSELF.

27:48.797 --> 27:51.452
SO...YOU KILLED THEM ALL.

27:51.452 --> 27:53.715
I DIDN'T KILL
MY GRANDFATHER.

27:53.715 --> 27:56.500
THAT'S NOT ON ME.
THAT WAS HIS CHOICE.

27:56.500 --> 27:58.720
HE WAS DYING
OF CANCER, BILL.

27:58.720 --> 28:01.592
HE WANTED TO GO OUT
ON HIS OWN TERMS --

28:01.592 --> 28:04.421
ONE MORE FINAL ACT
OF DEFIANCE.

28:04.421 --> 28:06.162
[ SCOFFS ]

28:06.162 --> 28:07.598
IF I WAS IN HIS POSITION,

28:07.598 --> 28:09.905
DOOMED TO A SLOW
AND MEANINGLESS DEATH,

28:09.905 --> 28:12.168
I'D DO THE SAME THING.

28:12.168 --> 28:13.648
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:13.648 --> 28:18.914
BOY, YOU ARE...INSANE.

28:22.004 --> 28:25.442
NO.
I'M JUST EVOLVED.

28:27.053 --> 28:31.100
HUMAN LIFE ISN'T AS VALUABLE
AS YOU THINK IT IS, WILKY.

28:31.100 --> 28:33.276
YOU KNOW THERE
ARE SEVEN BILLION PEOPLE

28:33.276 --> 28:34.756
WALKING AROUND THIS PLANET?

28:34.756 --> 28:37.977
AND WE'RE GROWING EXPONENTIALLY
YEAR BY YEAR.

28:37.977 --> 28:42.024
HUMANITY IS ON THE VERTICAL PART
OF THE "S" CURVE.

28:42.024 --> 28:45.288
IT'S COMPLETELY
UNSUSTAINABLE.

28:45.288 --> 28:49.945
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO CULL
THE HERD, PICK THE WINNERS.

28:49.945 --> 28:52.556
PEOPLE ARE GONNA HAVE TO DIE

28:52.556 --> 28:55.037
FOR THE REST OF US
TO SURVIVE.

28:55.037 --> 28:59.389
I'M JUST GETTING
A HEAD START.

29:07.006 --> 29:09.399
Man: I'LL GIVE HIM A CALL,
THANKS.

29:09.399 --> 29:12.185
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

29:29.506 --> 29:31.073
[ SIGHS ]

29:31.073 --> 29:32.379
Molk: MR. BLUNT.

29:32.379 --> 29:34.773
HEY, HOW YOU DOING?

29:34.773 --> 29:37.297
SAYS HE NEEDS TO TALK
TO HILDY AND TERRY.

29:37.297 --> 29:38.864
YEAH.

29:38.864 --> 29:41.475
HILDY,
SOMEONE HERE TO SEE YOU.

29:47.133 --> 29:49.352
FOUND HIM
IN THE LOBBY.

29:52.529 --> 29:54.270
YOU'RE UP EARLY.

29:54.270 --> 29:57.578
YEAH, I, UH -- I LEARNED SOME
INFORMATION LATE LAST NIGHT

29:57.578 --> 29:59.928
ABOUT THE DEATH
OF MY FATHER.

29:59.928 --> 30:01.756
I FELT I SHOULD COME IN
FIRST THING.

30:01.756 --> 30:03.236
Terry:
MM. YOU BEAT US TO IT.

30:03.236 --> 30:05.194
WE WERE, UH,
JUST GONNA COME SEE YOU.

30:06.456 --> 30:07.980
WOULD YOU MIND
FOLLOWING US?

30:07.980 --> 30:09.982
SURE.
ALL RIGHT.

30:27.564 --> 30:29.610
YEAH, WELL, WHY WOULD
SALTER AND WILKERSON

30:29.610 --> 30:31.655
WANT TO KILL
KEVIN NEYERS?
YEAH.

30:31.655 --> 30:33.353
WELL,
THEIR ENTIRE NET WORTH

30:33.353 --> 30:35.746
WAS IN APPLSN STOCK OPTIONS
I'D GIVEN THEM.

30:35.746 --> 30:38.619
AND ACCORDING TO BILL,
WHEN THEY LEARNED

30:38.619 --> 30:40.708
THAT NEYERS
WAS BLACKMAILING ME

30:40.708 --> 30:43.145
AND THREATENING
TO DERAIL THE I.P.O.,

30:43.145 --> 30:45.713
THEY TOOK MATTERS
INTO THEIR OWN HANDS.

30:45.713 --> 30:47.933
WHY WOULD WILKERSON CONFESS
ALL THIS TO YOU?

30:47.933 --> 30:49.978
HE WAS DESPERATE.

30:49.978 --> 30:52.633
I MEAN, HE'S LOST HIS MARRIAGE.
HE'S BROKE.

30:52.633 --> 30:55.418
I MEAN, COME ON, HE WAS WILLING
TO WEAR A BUG

30:55.418 --> 30:58.595
BECAUSE HE'S SO TERRIFIED
OF GOING TO PRISON.

30:58.595 --> 31:01.642
SO, I TOLD HIM
THAT HE COULD KEEP HIS JOB,

31:01.642 --> 31:04.558
AND I'D LOOK AFTER ALL
OF HIS MONEY AND LEGAL BILLS,

31:04.558 --> 31:06.516
BUT ONLY IF HE TOLD ME
THE TRUTH.

31:06.516 --> 31:07.866
ARE YOU DONE?

31:07.866 --> 31:09.128
I'M SORRY.

31:09.128 --> 31:10.694
I'M JUST WONDERING

31:10.694 --> 31:12.740
HOW YOU EXPECT US TO BELIEVE
ANYTHING YOU SAY ANYMORE.

31:12.740 --> 31:14.307
I'LL TAKE
A LIE-DETECTOR TEST.

31:14.307 --> 31:16.526
DO YOU THINK YOU COULD GET HIM
TO CONFESS AGAIN?

31:16.526 --> 31:18.659
YOU MEAN WEAR A WIRE?YEAH.

31:18.659 --> 31:21.967
NO. AFTER LAST NIGHT,
I DOUBT THAT WOULD WORK.

31:21.967 --> 31:25.318
DO YOU THINK WILKERSON
AND SALTER TALK?

31:25.318 --> 31:27.320
SURE. WOULDN'T SURPRISE ME.

31:27.320 --> 31:28.625
Hildy:
HEY, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

31:28.625 --> 31:30.279
YOU THINK WE COULD GET
A BUG ON SALTER?

31:30.279 --> 31:31.498
SALTER?

31:31.498 --> 31:33.108
Blunt: I MEAN,
HE'S ONE OF YOU.

31:33.108 --> 31:36.503
WOULDN'T HE, YOU KNOW, SMELL
THAT COMING A MILE AWAY?

31:36.503 --> 31:38.548
ALL RIGHT,
BUT WHAT IF IT WASN'T A BUG?

31:38.548 --> 31:41.725
WHAT IF -- CHECK THIS OUT.
I FORGET WHAT PAGE IT IS.

31:41.725 --> 31:44.859
THERE'S AN ARTICLE IN THERE, UH,
THAT TALKS ABOUT THE N.S.A.

31:44.859 --> 31:46.252
TAKING A REGULAR SMARTPHONE

31:46.252 --> 31:48.471
AND TURNING IT
INTO A RECORDING DEVICE,

31:48.471 --> 31:51.039
UH, THAT YOU CAN USE,
UH, BY REMOTE.UH-HUH.

31:51.039 --> 31:53.215
NOW, I'M NOT A TECHIE
OR A--

31:53.215 --> 31:55.739
BUT DO YOU THINK THAT
THAT WOULD BE POSSIBLE?

31:55.739 --> 31:56.871
COULD WE DO THAT?

32:03.312 --> 32:04.531
SURE.

32:04.531 --> 32:07.403
REALLY?YEAH. WHY NOT?

32:07.403 --> 32:10.102
I MEAN, A PHONE IS
JUST A COMPUTER, RIGHT?RIGHT.

32:10.102 --> 32:12.626
IT CAN PENETRATED
JUST LIKE ANY LAPTOP.

32:12.626 --> 32:14.758
I MEAN,
ALL YOU'D NEED TO DO

32:14.758 --> 32:17.587
IS HACK THROUGH THE LOGIN
INTO THE O.S.

32:17.587 --> 32:20.068
AND DROP A PIECE OF N.S.A.
MALWARE INTO THE SYSTEM UPDATE.

32:20.068 --> 32:21.504
IT'S PRETTY SIMPLE.

32:21.504 --> 32:24.290
BUT WOULDN'T YOU NEED
A FEDERAL WARRANT?

32:24.290 --> 32:28.468
OH, YOU MEAN...

32:28.468 --> 32:30.383
SOMETHING LIKE THIS?

32:32.515 --> 32:34.300
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

32:34.300 --> 32:35.779
[ SIGHS ]

32:44.571 --> 32:46.660
[ RECORDER BEEPS ]

32:46.660 --> 32:50.577
Blunt:
I JUST NUDGED CINDY TOWARDS
THOSE PROBABLE OUTCOMES.

32:52.231 --> 32:53.580
[ CHUCKLES]

32:53.580 --> 32:56.061
IT WAS SLOPPY,
BUT EFFECTIVE.

32:56.061 --> 32:59.238
NOW, THE WAY
THAT I KILLED MY FATHER --

32:59.238 --> 33:00.674
THAT WAS A WORK OF ART.

33:00.674 --> 33:02.067
[ RECORDER BEEPS ]

33:02.067 --> 33:03.590
ERICH MAXWELL BLUNT,

33:03.590 --> 33:05.026
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST FOR
THE MURDER OF KEVIN NEYERS.

33:05.026 --> 33:07.986
ANYTHING YOU SAY CAN
AND WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU

33:07.986 --> 33:09.335
IN A COURT OF LAW.

33:09.335 --> 33:11.206
GET WARREN DANIELS
ON THE PHONE, NOW!

33:11.206 --> 33:12.773
YOU DO HAVE THE RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY.

33:12.773 --> 33:14.079
IF YOU CAN'T AFFORD
AN ATTORNEY,

33:14.079 --> 33:15.428
ONE WILL BE APPOINTED
FOR YOU.

33:15.428 --> 33:16.733
AFFORD ONE?!

33:16.733 --> 33:18.257
I'M A BILLIONAIRE.

33:18.257 --> 33:21.086
THIS IS MY HOUSE.
THIS IS MY GAME!

33:21.086 --> 33:23.088
[ GRUNTS ]

33:23.088 --> 33:26.178
GAME OVER.

33:34.403 --> 33:36.101
Woman: THE SAN FRANCISCO
HOMICIDE UNIT,

33:36.101 --> 33:37.624
LED BY LIEUTENANT JIM KOTO

33:37.624 --> 33:39.800
AND INSPECTORS ENGLISH
AND MULLIGAN,

33:39.800 --> 33:41.758
WORKED CLOSELY
WITH THE MEDICAL EXAMINER,

33:41.758 --> 33:44.326
C.S.I., AND OUR CRIME LAB...

33:44.326 --> 33:46.285
Man: APPLSN STOCK
IS IN FREE FALL SINCE BLUNT'S
STUNNING ARREST THIS MORNING.

33:46.285 --> 33:47.938
THANK YOU, MAGGIE.

33:47.938 --> 33:50.637
SHARES CURRENTLY TRADING
FOR LESS THAN A DOLLAR

33:50.637 --> 33:52.639
AS NEWS OF HIS TAPED CONFESSION
TO TWO MURDERS

33:52.639 --> 33:54.945
PUTS THE FUTURE OF A--[ REMOTE CLICKS ]

33:58.775 --> 34:00.516
HE WANTS TO HIRE YOU.

34:02.779 --> 34:06.740
AND I WANT TO GO ON A DATE
WITH BEYONCé.

34:06.740 --> 34:11.484
SOME THINGS IN LIFE, DAVID,
JUST AREN'T IN THE CARDS.

34:11.484 --> 34:13.921
THE QUESTION IS,

34:13.921 --> 34:18.273
WHY ARE YOUSTILL WORKING
FOR THIS SOCIOPATH?

34:18.273 --> 34:20.145
EVERY MAN DESERVES A LAWYER.

34:20.145 --> 34:22.669
NO LAWYER DESERVES HIM.

34:22.669 --> 34:25.106
LOOK,
IF IT'S ABOUT MONEY --WHAT MONEY?

34:25.106 --> 34:26.107
HE HAS NO MONEY.

34:26.107 --> 34:28.675
BY THE END OF THE DAY,

34:28.675 --> 34:31.982
THE ONLY THING HE'LL BE C.E.O.
OF IS HIS JAIL CELL.

34:33.810 --> 34:36.944
YOU KNOW THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN A C.E.O. AND A CRIMINAL?

34:36.944 --> 34:39.338
VENTURE CAPITAL.

34:39.338 --> 34:41.470
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:41.470 --> 34:44.995
YOU, MY FRIEND,
ARE LIVING PROOF

34:44.995 --> 34:49.435
THAT INSIDE OF EVERY CYNIC
IS A DISILLUSIONED IDEALIST.

34:55.005 --> 34:58.357
WHEN WE FIRST MET
IN WASHINGTON,

34:58.357 --> 35:01.403
DID YOU EVER THINK
WE'D END UP HERE?

35:01.403 --> 35:03.971
ME, YES. YOU, NO.

35:03.971 --> 35:05.712
YOU WERE CHIEF COUNSEL

35:05.712 --> 35:08.758
FOR THE SENATE JUDICIARY
COMMITTEE AT, WHAT, 34?
MM.

35:08.758 --> 35:11.021
I THOUGHT YOU'D END UP
ON THE SUPREME COURT.

35:11.021 --> 35:14.024
[ CHUCKLES ]
SO DID MY MOTHER.

35:14.024 --> 35:16.331
JUSTICE DANIELS,
WHAT HAPPENED?

35:19.160 --> 35:21.293
I DISCOVERED
I LIKE MONEY.

35:22.990 --> 35:24.339
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:24.339 --> 35:27.037
YOU DON'T FLY PLANES,

35:27.037 --> 35:29.605
DRIVE FANCY CARS,
TAKE EXPENSIVE VACATIONS.

35:29.605 --> 35:31.433
WHAT DID YOU DO
WITH IT ALL?

35:31.433 --> 35:34.915
MY MONEY?
OH, I KEEP IT.

35:34.915 --> 35:36.699
WHY?

35:36.699 --> 35:38.745
SO I HAVE IT.

35:38.745 --> 35:43.271
SO I CAN AFFORD TO SAY NO
TO MEN LIKE ERICH BLUNT.

35:46.883 --> 35:51.192
I THOUGHT HE WAS INNOCENT.
I REALLY DID.

35:53.194 --> 35:56.110
I DIDN'T,
NOT FOR A MINUTE.

35:56.110 --> 35:59.679
HE PASSED
A LIE-DETECTOR TEST.

36:03.161 --> 36:06.903
HE DIDN'T PASS
THE LIE-DETECTOR TEST.

36:09.384 --> 36:11.908
I JUST MADE THAT UP.

36:22.092 --> 36:24.660
[ BUZZER ]

36:40.502 --> 36:43.026
IS IT TRUE --

36:43.026 --> 36:44.941
WHAT YOU SAID TO BILL,

36:44.941 --> 36:48.728
WHAT THEY CLAIM THEY HAVE YOU
SAYING ON TAPE?

36:48.728 --> 36:51.426
OF COURSE NOT, DAVID.

36:51.426 --> 36:52.775
FIRST THING WE SHOULD DO

36:52.775 --> 36:55.430
IS FILE A MOTION
TO THROW THIS TAPE OUT.

36:55.430 --> 36:58.781
ON WHAT GROUNDS?

36:58.781 --> 37:00.174
[ SCOFFS ]

37:00.174 --> 37:02.089
ILLEGAL WIRETAP.
WHATEVER.

37:02.089 --> 37:03.960
DANIELS WILL FIGURE IT OUT.

37:03.960 --> 37:06.789
DANIELS IS NOT TAKING
THE CASE.

37:06.789 --> 37:08.226
[ SCOFFS ]

37:08.226 --> 37:10.271
WAIT, WHAT? WHY?

37:10.271 --> 37:12.839
WHY? BECAUSE YOU'RE BROKE,
ERICH.

37:12.839 --> 37:14.449
YOUR COMPANY IS GONE.

37:14.449 --> 37:16.495
SALTER IS GONE.
IVANA IS GONE.

37:16.495 --> 37:19.498
WILKERSON IS GONE.
DANIELS IS GONE.

37:31.727 --> 37:33.555
[ SIGHS ]

37:33.555 --> 37:36.558
WELL, AT LEAST
I'VE STILL GOT YOU.

37:40.649 --> 37:42.825
NO, YOU DON'T.

37:46.351 --> 37:50.833
I'M RESIGNING...
AS OF RIGHT NOW.

37:53.967 --> 37:55.664
WHAT?

37:55.664 --> 37:57.187
JUST CAME IN
TO SAY GOODBYE.

37:59.842 --> 38:01.975
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

38:21.690 --> 38:26.216
WHY? TELL ME WHY.

38:26.216 --> 38:29.350
I BELIEVED IN YOU, ERICH.

38:29.350 --> 38:32.179
I BELIEVED IN YOU.

38:32.179 --> 38:34.399
I DON'T ANYMORE.

38:35.400 --> 38:37.489
[ BUZZER ]

39:18.573 --> 39:21.446
WE DID GOOD.

39:21.446 --> 39:23.622
YEAH. I GUESS.

39:23.622 --> 39:26.842
UH, IT FEELS WEIRD TO BE
CELEBRATING, THOUGH.

39:26.842 --> 39:29.758
[ SIGHS ]
WHY? WE DID OUR JOB.

39:29.758 --> 39:30.846
WE WERE RIGHT.

39:30.846 --> 39:34.807
I KNOW.
JUST...THAT GUY.

39:34.807 --> 39:37.549
I FEEL LIKE...

39:37.549 --> 39:41.291
HE'S THE CLOSEST THING
I'VE EVER SEEN TO PURE EVIL.

39:41.291 --> 39:45.208
WHAT HE DID IS JUST NOT --

39:45.208 --> 39:46.862
NOT HUMAN.

39:46.862 --> 39:49.474
[ SIGHS ]

39:49.474 --> 39:51.258
THAT'S PROBABLY
WHAT MAKES HIM HUMAN.

39:51.258 --> 39:53.608
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

39:53.608 --> 39:54.957
[ SIGHS ]

39:54.957 --> 39:58.134
PEOPLE LIKE BLUNT -- EVIL --

39:58.134 --> 40:00.485
IT'S LIKE A HUNGER,
YOU KNOW,

40:00.485 --> 40:02.965
A HOLE THAT THEY NEED
TO FILL.

40:02.965 --> 40:07.274
I THINK IT'S THEIR NATURE.

40:07.274 --> 40:09.668
THEY NEED IT,

40:09.668 --> 40:12.758
KIND OF LIKE YOU AND I --

40:12.758 --> 40:14.890
LIKE YOU AND I NEED LOVE.

40:20.505 --> 40:22.463
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

40:24.422 --> 40:27.468
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]YEAH?

40:33.213 --> 40:35.476
OH, NO.

40:57.542 --> 41:00.370
Blunt: [ Echoing ] HE WANTED
TO GO OUT ON HIS OWN TERMS --

41:00.370 --> 41:02.155
ONE MORE FINAL ACT
OF DEFIANCE.

41:02.155 --> 41:03.852
IF I WAS IN HIS POSITION,

41:03.852 --> 41:06.507
DOOMED TO A SLOW
AND MEANINGLESS DEATH,

41:06.507 --> 41:08.683
I'D DO THE SAME THING.

41:24.612 --> 41:26.222
